# results

**Interface Property**

The results from an autocomplete request.

## Declaration

```swift
results: SearchAutocompleteResult[];
```

## Discussion

This property contains an array of [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResult] objects corresponding to the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResponse/query].

## Response

- **query**: The query string used to perform the autocomplete request.
